Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.66,0:00:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦总会迎来终点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是多么开心的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是多么可怕的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暖和的被窝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在母亲轻柔的唤醒下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.72,0:00:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦随之终结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直一直未曾改变过 清晨的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而如今…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}那永无止境的梦是从什么时候开始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再哭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是说句话啊 亚由亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕 才不是亚由亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 不是能好好地把话说清楚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被盯着也很麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非我长得很像你才出生就分别了的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然肚子饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 给你买点吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想吃的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的吗 你喜欢吃的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:02:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲷鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鲷鱼烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 在这里等着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好地等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你说要等着的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真乖 真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为鲷鱼烧是刚烧好的时候最美味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃 快吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你刚才眼泪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs54}然后我也是呢 捏了一把汗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 为什么要哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想说的话 今天就不问了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 亚由亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶 才不是亚由亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样没法走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲷鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想吃鲷鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么喜欢的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要在一起吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么的话 明天 一样的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在车站前的长椅那等着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会骗偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不骗你 我一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 约定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉钩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不拉钩我也会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉钩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:05:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜 吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那个没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来报复我 却又失败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这块蒟蒻是你的夜宵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么快吃下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是正想吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 不用客气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 肚子已经饱了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费食物的话 会遭报应的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴她在吃蒟蒻 说是夜宵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒟蒻？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子已经那么饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 给你做点吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子已经不饿了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是 专挑妨碍睡眠的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天必须要整理好这些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早上的问候就是「啊呜」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子到现在一直都很涨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你晚上硬要吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有硬要吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是要放在祐一的脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脸什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我等着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还要给名雪送去她忘记带的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 今天也有田径部的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 由我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田径部的部长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是什么样的情景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我拿来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是不错的建筑物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这所学校很重视社团活动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为马上就是大赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以稍微参观下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在角落那边的话 没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相泽君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要参加社团活动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和名雪一样的呢 明明是假日还那么认真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是名雪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想呆在家里罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和家里人吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相泽君 已经习惯这个学校了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还是半生不熟 不过还可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 同一间教室里有认识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说名雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以太让名雪困扰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有她 你才能这么快的融入班级
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好感谢她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪她虽然一副漫不经心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有时候也很倔强呢 要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团活动也是每天都练习到精疲力尽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那么能睡原来是因为这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为那个是天生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思 难得的休息日还让你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 这不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨一个人拿这么多东西肯定很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 有祐一在真的帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是祐一君 又见面啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕 又撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就别怨我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个完全不认识的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕 真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非祐一君讨厌偶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又吃霸王餐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有 这是刚才鲷鱼烧大叔送的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明给人家添了那么多麻烦… 大叔还真是个好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个活泼的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水濑秋子阿姨 我寄居处的家主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家主是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里最伟大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 又学到一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 也为我介绍下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月宫亚由 我认识的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月宫亚由？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我的错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一君 接下来打算做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经准备回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天必须要收拾搬家的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么偶也来帮忙好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 昨天你帮偶找东西 今天算是还人情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:13:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还挺老实的呢 还以为你会像平常一样一头冲进来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事只是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 快出来吧 我来给你介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽渡真琴 和我一样也是寄住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样子很失礼的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下来打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶叫月宫亚由 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽…泽渡真琴 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说 你也来帮我收拾行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴也要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是寄居的人 做这点小事也是应该的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴妹妹 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真没有力气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜 要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是祐一君的房间呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死啦 连腰都直不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才搬了一只箱子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下我来搬好了 你们把里面的东西整理好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吗 鲷鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点冷了 不介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌甜食吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 会变胖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是累了 待会再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然三人齐心协力的话 马上就弄好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和真琴只会把东西翻得乱七八糟而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 多少帮了一点忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 多谢你们帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了来帮忙却反而添乱的话 好像偶是骗子似的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由 东西找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 具体怎么回事还不清楚 总之像在找很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次祐一君帮过偶 今天算是还人情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 能早日找到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 偶回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人能回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没和真琴妹妹打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她大概是午睡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时欢迎你来玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:18:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吃海绵蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 已经回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要帮我按摩吗 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那等我洗完澡再麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是按摩的事 我是来要回借你的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笔记？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是借给你了吗 因为你说这边学校进度比之前的快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘在学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋了 要做作业了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉 明天去学校还你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是再见什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想问你呢 现在该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再议吧 今天早点睡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到明天就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果祐一没有完成作业的话 也一样会伤脑筋的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于这种事 我已经超脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没超脱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不好好作做作业的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个老师可是很严格的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 你想让我马上到学校去拿笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是非要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校大概已经关门了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有还开着的窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有的话 打碎玻璃进去就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面很冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 就当作是顺便去慢跑好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香里碎碎念的让我不要给你添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 因为我的事情让你要再到学校跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自作自受 别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 赶快回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是讨伐魔物之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.55,0:23:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你 马上退学」可以这样说的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.85,0:23:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不想呢 那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.81,0:23:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨伐魔物之人 讨伐魔物之人 讨伐魔物…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.52,0:23:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨 真擅长料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那么说之前 你最好先尝尝她做的特制果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.05,0:24:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 真的就像是哥哥一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.24,0:24:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为会被杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.91,0:24:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.20,0:24:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
